# ─── API gateway local gitignore ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# The root .gitignore already covers most of these patterns; this file makes
# the same rules explicit at the service level so they're discoverable when
# working in this directory and so the service is self-describing if it is
# ever moved out of the monorepo.

# ─── Local runtime data ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Reference JSON datasets (university list, IDX, fashion, etc.) live next to
# test.db and uploads/ in data/ — we only ignore the dynamic artefacts.
data/test.db
data/superapp.db
data/superapp.db-journal
data/*.db
data/*.db-journal
data/uploads/

# ─── Go build artefacts ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.exe
*.exe~
*.test
*.out
api-gateway
api-gateway-new
test-build

# ─── Local logs / scratch ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
api.err
api.log
run-test.ps1

# ─── Python (in case a tooling helper script is added later) ────────────────
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.venv/
venv/

# ─── Secrets / local env ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.local
